data.description: Short Sale! Introducing elegance and architectural charm! This home was recently built just a few months ago and is awaiting its new owner. Featuring three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an open floor concept that is perfect to entertain and host family gatherings. The kitchen is a chefs dream with ample quartz counter space, stainless steel appliances, and an island with a sink. Located on a corner lot within the KB Home community this home comes with several energy efficient features such as dual pane windows, insulation, LED lighting, smart thermostat, low flow toilets and showerheads, and solar panels. The backyard has recently installed pavers and is awaiting for the finishing touches to complete your own private oasis. Don't let this one pass you by!
